OL,5, Evhen Ryabukon patted the coffin       
OL,6, gently, and appeared to be having a    
OL,7, final conversation with his son. He    
OL,8, broke down, over and over again, before
OL,9, he could finish.                       
OL,11,FHis wife Inna, steeling herself,       
OL,12,Fadjusted the framed photo of a smiling,
OL,13,Fyoung boy placed on the coffin - a     
OL,14,Fmother's last act of care.             
